🔥 3. Real Interview Optimization Example
Problem:- 
Find high-value customers

❌ Slow Query:
SELECT *
FROM orders
WHERE customer_id IN (
  SELECT id FROM customers WHERE country = 'India'
);

✅ Optimized:
SELECT o.*
FROM orders o
JOIN customers c
ON o.customer_id = c.id
WHERE c.country = 'India';

# 👉 Why faster?
- Uses JOIN instead of subquery
- Better index usage

